    "question_id" : 20537845,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have the same problem. In my case I have two development environments open in the same time: Android Studio and Eclipse. After I close Eclipse and run the debug process again works well. Hope this help!</p>\n"
  }, {
