    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You may want to check your debugging setting in Dev Setting on your AVD. Take a look at the following picture: </p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/p1XC2.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/p1XC2.jpg\" alt=\"developer settings example\"></a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/p1XC2.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\">developer settings example</a></p>\n"
