    "last_activity_date" : 1594797685,
    "creation_date" : 1594797685,
    "answer_id" : 62909537,
    "question_id" : 20537845,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Without restarting the device, I was able to fix this issue by going to &quot;Developer Options&quot; and then first &quot;disabling&quot; and then &quot;enabling&quot;-</p>\n<ol>\n<li>USB Debugging</li>\n<li>Wireless ADB Debugging (Since I debug over the Wifi)</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/vUZo4.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/vUZo4.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 18656420,
      "reputation" : 109,
      "user_id" : 13598744,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/bc64bb09f5270d3cfaf0c6c83127f29a?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Vismay Viradiya",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/13598744/vismay-viradiya"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1614342593,
    "last_edit_date" : 1614342593,
    "creation_date" : 1614313910,
    "answer_id" : 66380160,
    "question_id" : 20537845,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Save everything using ctrl+s or &quot;File&quot; -&gt; &quot;Save all&quot;. Go to your project directory and delete the .gradle folder then refresh window using F5. After this step, open project in Android Studio and run the application using Shift+F10 or Run -&gt; &quot;Run app&quot;. Then it should run in normal mode.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 14967979,
      "reputation" : 21,
      "user_id" : 10805683,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/487894d17ea864f77a68ec37028ccd4b?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Jos&#233; Torres",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/10805683/jos%c3%a9-torres"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1634913058,
    "creation_date" : 1634913058,
    "answer_id" : 69678658,
    "question_id" : 20537845,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In my case the debug was stuck and didn't advance. So I remove the &quot;.lldb&quot; folder in the path &quot;C:\\Users{user}.lldb&quot; and now is working.</p>\n"
  } ],
